tilegame
tilegame contains the base classes to create a tile based game.
  • Classes in tilegame used by game2048
    Class
    Description
    GameObserver
    This interface class allows the programmers to create observers to observe a TileGameModel
    TileGame
    The abstract class TileGame allows programmers to develop their own tile based game by supplying a TileGameModel, a TileGameGUI, and a TileGameController.
    TileGameController
    The public class TileGameController allows you to modify a game model.
    TileGameGUI
    The abstract class TileGameGUI allows programmers to represent their TileGameModel graphically.
    TileGameModel
    The class TileGameModel allows programmers to develop their own tile game model and manipulate it.
